sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as MockInterview UI
    participant Speech as Web Speech API
    participant Backend as Next.js<br/>/api/mock_int
    participant LLM as Groq API
    participant TTS as Speech Synthesis

    User->>UI: Clicks "Start Interview"
    UI->>UI: Initialize system prompt<br/>with topic + difficulty
    
    UI->>Backend: POST message: "__start__"<br/>+ system prompt
    Backend->>LLM: Create chat message<br/>with system context
    LLM->>Backend: Return first question
    Backend->>UI: Return parsed JSON<br/>{message, end}
    
    UI->>UI: Append to history<br/>Display question
    UI->>TTS: Speak question aloud
    TTS->>User: Audio output
    
    User->>Speech: Click microphone<br/>Start listening
    User->>User: Say answer
    Speech->>UI: Return transcript
    
    UI->>UI: Append user message<br/>Set status: "Thinking..."
    UI->>Backend: POST user answer<br/>+ full history + system prompt
    
    Backend->>LLM: Send conversation history<br/>to Groq with constraints
    LLM->>Backend: Return feedback<br/>+ next question<br/>{message, end}
    Backend->>UI: Parsed response
    
    UI->>UI: Append assistant message<br/>to history
    UI->>TTS: Speak feedback
    TTS->>User: Audio output
    UI->>UI: Increment question counter
    
    alt Interview Complete
        LLM->>Backend: Return {end: true}
        Backend->>UI: Final message
        UI->>TTS: Speak closing message
        UI->>UI: Set finishedRef = true
        UI->>UI: onClose() callback
        UI-->>User: Close modal
    else Continue Interview
        User->>Speech: Click microphone again
        Speech-->>UI: Loop repeats
    end
